name: Magicians' Combination
desc: Once per turn, when a card or effect is activated: You can Tribute 1 "Dark Magician" or 1 "Dark Magician Girl"; Special Summon 1 "Dark Magician" or 1 "Dark Magician Girl" from your hand or GY with a different name from the Tributed monster, and if you do, negate the activated effect. If this face-up card in the Spell & Trap Zone is sent to the GY: You can destroy 1 card on the field.
